Eventually, Microsoft Office became the dominant business suite, with a market share far exceeding that of its competitors.  McCracken, Harry. &quot; A Peek at Office Upgrade&quot;  ,  PCWorld.com , September 13, 2000
     . Retrieved on July 04, 2006
